node.text:
Thank you @sentosa_island for the wonderful experience! We’ll never forget this! So thankful to be able to celebrate this special day despite the current situation. ☺️
Thank you friends for joining in celebrating this special day with us. ————————————————————————————— Posted @withregram • @sentosa_island Spoiler: she said yes! .
We’ve just helped a lovely couple celebrate their special day at their beautiful beach wedding on #VirtualSentosa 👰🏻🏝
.
Swipe to see how we got the wedding bells ringin’ 🔔 👉
.
#MakeTime #VirtualSentosa #AnimalCrossing #stayhomeforSG
We're so glad we helped make this special day happen for you both 🥺 See y'all soon! Stay safe ❤️
